Package Summary 
Package Description
<Unnamed>
Provides classes for the test scripts related to the Model component of the Model-View-Controller architecture
cards
Provides the classes for the cards
cards.action_cards
Provides the classes for the action cards, which ask the player to either pay to or collect from money from another player or the Bank
cards.action_cards.collect_from_bank
Provides classes for the action cards that ask the player to collect money from the Bank
cards.action_cards.collect_from_player
Provides classes for the action cards that ask the player to collect money from another player
cards.action_cards.pay_bank
Provides classes for the action cards that ask the player to pay money to the Bank
cards.action_cards.pay_player
Provides classes for the action cards that ask the player to pay money to another player
cards.blue_cards
Provides the classes for the blue cards, which ask the player to either pay to or collect from money from another player or the Bank depending on the presence of a career match
cards.career_cards
Provides the classes for the career cards, which dictates the player's career, degree requirement (whether it is required or not), and maximum number of pay raises
controllers
Provides classes for the controllers connecting the front- and back-ends in relation to the Model-View-Controller architecture
core
Provides the classes for the central game components (namely, those implementing the player, bank, discard pile, number wheel, board, and game master) and the interfaces implemented by some of the classes
decks
Provides the classes for the card decks
gui
Provides classes for the graphical user interface, corresponding to the View in the Model-View-Controller architecture
spaces
Provides classes for the spaces on which the player lands
spaces.green_spaces
Provides classes for the green spaces on which the player receives the effect of either a pay day or a pay raise
spaces.magenta_spaces
Provides classes for the magenta spaces that execute special events depending on the type
